{"tid":1457523,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我係散水撚，我認我係衰仔。所以請大家再入過機場！","createTime":"2019-08-12T11:49:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T12:05:15.000Z","uid":40072,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e218195eaf2d9b8f8a08e50536a3cc745861e8d6","tid":1457523,"uid":40072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:49:20.000Z","msg":"屌，下晝見到咁多狗入機場，又出埋畜龍，我真心擔心大家。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我諗好多人同我一樣已經對班爛仔有恐懼.......<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我認衰，所以我而家死返入機場，手足等我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n機場見！放工嘅快啲嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65bfe94683a810acc72352d6087110de2b281f10","tid":1457523,"uid":40072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:54:56.000Z","msg":"返入機場呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9020b2917